description.en:
TraDove platform will connects business partners with its business social network. The next generation platform will utilize blockchain and AI driven social networking technologies to further shorten the corporate buyer & seller discovery cycle, enhance B2B transparency, expand user trust, and allow for company-to-company precision advertising. Additionally, BBCoin will provide a better payment instrument for international trade. They have been in business for 5 years and now have 250K corporate users worldwide. 
In development.
